Standards-Version: 3.7.2
Section: libs

Package: libsigar
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: System Information Gatherer and Reporter library
 SIGAR (System Information Gatherer and Reporter) is a cross-platform, cross-language library and command-line tool for accessing operating system and hardware level information in Java, Perl and .NET.

Package: libsigar-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libsigar (= ${Source-Version})
Description: System Information Gatherer and Reporter library headers
 SIGAR (System Information Gatherer and Reporter) is a cross-platform, cross-language library and command-line tool for accessing operating system and hardware level information in Java, Perl and .NET.
